body: Hello! I got an error message when trying to load this RData file: "GC18unionAnno.Rdata" in the Pre Processing R code and indeed the file is really small (5kB)... I guess this old file was removed . Where could I find an alternative one for the replication of the analysis?  Thank you very much!
